        "Use Git server-side `post-receive` hooks to execute automated test and deployment scripts directly upon pushing code.",
        "Deploy code efficiently using `git --work-tree` and `git checkout -f` to extract the latest commits to targeted directories.",
        "Replaces heavy CI/CD systems like Jenkins or GitHub Actions with lightweight shell scripts, reducing infrastructure overhead for small projects."
      ]
